    • resolveUrl

      public URL resolveUrl(String urlSpec) throws InspectusException
      urlString could be in 2 forms: - with URL protocol 
      http://hostname/foo.html
      - without URL protocol 
      /foo.html
      Either form should be accepted. When the protocol is omitted, then the baseTopPage is refered to supplement the protocol+host+port of the url to return the baseTopPage is
      Parameters:
      urlSpec - e.g, "http://host/foo.html" or "/foo.html" or "foo.html"
      Returns:
      URL
      Throws:
      InspectusException - when urlSpec is malformed
